dcterms:description: The Multimodal Brain Tumor Segmentation Challenge (BraTS) 2020 training dataset was used to train multiple U-net like neural networks for brain tumor segmentation, focusing on enhancing the accuracy of delineating tumor subregions.
dcterms:title: Multimodal Brain Tumor Segmentation Challenge (BraTS) 2020 training dataset

dcterms:description: The online validation dataset was used to evaluate the performance of the models during the segmentation challenge.
dcterms:title: Online validation dataset

dcterms:description: The testing dataset was used to assess the final performance of the models in the segmentation challenge.
dcterms:title: Testing dataset

dcterms:description: The TCGA-GBM collection provides segmentation labels and radiomic features for the pre-operative scans of glioblastoma patients, facilitating research in tumor analysis.
